metadata.name: The Bloody bride
metadata.description:
The playful atmosphere of The Bloody Bride provides an opening of respect for love.

She couldn't love a man so strongly
Even the prophets punished her for her dishonesty.

But the soon-to-be-married bride discovered disgusting things about her husband.
which is the demon she clings to.


Would she kill him or forgive him?
